PLUS with your Sunday Express, don’t miss the second pocket guide in this collection – the RSPB Beginner’s Guide to Bird Spotting: Country Walks. We’ve teamed up with the RSPB to bring you a guide chock full of birds you’re likely to see when you’re out and about in the countryside, and even some rarer species to watch out for! Whether you are looking to entertain the kids when on an adventure, or want to learn more about the birds which call our country landscapes home – don’t miss your weekend papers on Saturday April 2 and Sunday April 3, 2022 to pick up these amazing bird spotting pocket guides from the RSPB.